<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"/>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/base.css">
    <title>欢迎首页</title>
    {asset src="yee"}
    {literal}
    <script>
        Yee.on('xload', function (abc) {
            console.log('abc', abc);
        }, true);

        setTimeout(function () {
            Yee.emit('load','欢迎界面');
        }, 1000);

    </script>
    <style>
        html, body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: #F9F9F9;
        }

        h1 {
            height: 50px;
            line-height: 50px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e4eaec;
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #343434;
            padding: 0 28px;
        }

        .content {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
    {/literal}
</head>
<body>
<div class="sdopx-table-box">
    <h1>欢迎您登陆 <strong class="blu">{#webname#}</strong> 后台管理系统。</h1>
    <div class="content">
        <table width="97%" border="0" cellspacing="1" align="center" cellpadding="0">
            <tr>
                <td bgcolor="#FFFFFF" style="line-height: 25px; padding: 5px;">
                    <p><font color="#003399">使用时注意事项：<br/>
                        &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1.请确认你的登录是网管授权,未经授权的登录将视为非法登录。<br/>
                        &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2.本程序的改动,将直接关系前台网站页面的内容。<br/>
                        &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3.最高管理员有开放帐户的能力,是本站的最高权限,请注意保管好自已的密码。</font><br/>
                        <br/>
                        <br/>
                        <br/>
                    </p>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <input yee-module="number" type="text"/>
        </table>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
